data.title: World Championship Race
data.text:
World Championship Race 2024/2025

The top 32 of the Order of Merit will qualify. They will be joined by the top 32 not yet qualified players of the Pro Tour OoM and 32 International Qualifiers.

Includes provisional prize money for all remaining tournaments this season according to the current qualifying spots, even if qualification is not secure yet.

Cut-off: November 25, 2024. Updated after PC17.

Prize money in the tables is in units of Â£1,000.
